&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;The Data Products team is a startup&amp;nbsp;operating&amp;nbsp;inside&amp;nbsp;CentralReach.&amp;nbsp;We are&amp;nbsp;establishing&amp;nbsp;our own playbook&amp;nbsp;and processes&amp;nbsp;as we build.&amp;nbsp;You will inherit an existing ABI roadmap.&amp;nbsp;Your job is to own&amp;nbsp;it,&amp;nbsp;pressure test it against customer reality and our&amp;nbsp;new&amp;nbsp;data product&amp;nbsp;strategy and&amp;nbsp;rebuild it into something you stand behind.&amp;nbsp;You will&amp;nbsp;serve as the connective tissue between our customers, engineering and go-to-market teams&amp;nbsp;and grow into a strategic leader as the team scales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are looking for someone with low patience for&amp;nbsp;heavy&amp;nbsp;process&amp;nbsp;and high ownership mentality. If you move fast, communicate opinions clearly, and stay relentlessly focused on the customer, you will thrive here.&amp;nbsp;We believe AI tools are changing what&amp;nbsp;great product&amp;nbsp;management looks&amp;nbsp;like&amp;nbsp;and we want someone who believes that too. Not as a productivity bonus, but as a fundamentally&amp;nbsp;different way&amp;nbsp;to move from idea to delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
